title: Second Christmas
description: The Titans trick Starfire into believing in second Christmas with second Santa.

title: We're Off to Get Awards
description: During an awards ceremony, Robin is swept up by a tornado and arrives in a magical land.

title: Ghost with the Most
description: When the Halloween Spirit is kidnapped, the Titans must team with Beetlejuice to save the holiday.

title: Thumb War
description: As the other Titans engage in an all out thumb wrestling war, Starfire tries to broker peace.

title: Magic Man
description: In a quest to become a magic man, Beast Boy accidentally destroys Raven's spell book, so they must go find another one.

title: Carl SanPedro Part 2
description: Carl Sanpedro has struck again, this time in Jamaica, so the Titans take off for the Caribbean.

title: Bat Scouts
description: To reach the highest rank in the Bat Scouts, Robin teaches the other Titans important vigilante skills.

title: The Cast
description: After breaking his leg, Robin is confined to his room and spies through a telescope.

title: Kryponite
description: When Robin explains that knowing your weakness makes you a better superhero, Starfire journeys to find hers.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Four
description: To retrieve the final stem, the Titans must concur a virtual world full of increasingly harder obstacles.

title: Flashback Part 1
description: A flashback reveals how Robin formed the Teen Titans.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Two
description: In order to stop Ultralak, the Titans must find three music stems, but will need help from a local Miner to get the first stem away from the Sheriff.

title: Brain Flip
description: It's time for Beast Boy to leave, but the Doom Patrol try everything they can to get him to stay.

title: Mo' Money Mo' Problems
description: The Titans make Robin give them a tour of Wayne Manor and discover how fun it is to be rich.

title: Record Book
description: Starfire wants a world record, so she decides to grow her fingernails.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Justice League Edition Part 2
description: In order to be the most talented superhero team in the DC universe, Robin and Beast Boy must work together on a jazz performance.

title: Flashback Part 2
description: A flashback reveals how Robin changed from mild-mannered sidekick to quick-tempered leader.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Three
description: The Titans are horrified to learn that songs are being melted down and  polluting the landscape.

title: Carl SanPedro Part 1
description: The Titans fly to Los Angeles but end up in San Pedro, where Berto tells them about the villainous long shoreman, Carl Sanpedro.

title: Carl SanPedro Part 4
description: In the final epic showdown with Carl Sanpedro, the Titans head to Croatia, the home of dragons and ice zombies.

title: Crab Shenanigans
description: Beast Boy, Negative Girl, and Robotman start hanging out with some punk crabs but soon discover the crabs are up to no good.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Justice League Edition Part 1
description: The Justice League holds yet another talent competition, only this time they're facing off against the Titans.

title: Toddler Titans...Yay!
description: Control Freak thinks the Titans' humor is too juvenile for their time-slot, so he ages them down to a preschool show.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter One
description: The elderly Titans decide to take one last trip to the world of Night Begins to Shine only to encounter a new villian ruling the land, Ultralak.

title: The Return of Slade
description: Beast Boy and Cyborg insist on hiring a clown for a Titans party, even though Robin tells them that clowns are for little kids. When the clown fails to live up to their memories, Cyborg and Beast Boy decide to give the clown some cool updates.

title: Superhero Feud
description: Control Freak pits the Titans against the DC Superhero Girls to determine who is the best team in the universe.

title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

title: Huggbees
description: The Brain teams up with The Lobe, so the Titans enlist the help of Freakazoid to stop them.

title: Titans Go Casual
description: The Superhero Board of Authority institutes a dress code which leads the Titans to introduce Casual Tuesday.

title: That's What's Up
description: Beast Boy heads back east to visit his family, the Doom Patrol, and they decide to throw a clambake to celebrate.

title: The True Meaning of Christmas
description: Fed up with never getting presents from Santa, the Titans head to the north pole to take themselves off the Naughty List by any means necessary.

title: How's This for a Special? Spaaaace Part 1
description: After receiving a galactic crime alert, the Titans take off for an epic space adventure.

title: Brobots
description: Cyborg comes to visit Beast Boy, but once Cyborg realizes how much he and Robotman have in common, they become inseparable.

title: Bucket List
description: The Titans give Starfire a bucket list of activies to accomplish.

title: Carl SanPedro Part 3
description: The Titans travel to India to stop Carl Sanpedro and learn about the sport of cricket.

title: TV Knight 6
description: Batman is forced to go to the department store with Alfred, but runs off to watch TV with Commissioner Gordon.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Five
description: The Titans use to the stems to summon BER, but will it be enough to stop Ultralak?

title: Teen Titans Roar!
description: The Titans are outraged when their favorite cartoon is rebooted so they come up with a plan to get this new show off the air.

title: Egg Hunt
description: Robin still regrets not being able to find an Easter egg when he was a kid, so the Titans head to Gotham to solve this mystery.

title: Halloween vs. Christmas
description: When Santa tries to take over Halloween, it's up to the Titans and a few ghouls to stop him.

title: Christmas Crusaders
description: Santa Claus and Robin must stop the nefarious Coal Miner.

title: Rain on Your Wedding Day
description: While facing off with The Brain, Robin tries to teach the other Titans the proper definition of irony.

title: Walk Away
description: After the T-Car is destroyed in a fight, the Titans go to a used car lot to find another vehicle.

title: How's This for a Special? Spaaaace Part 2
description: The Titans have to stop Darkseid's latest scheme, but the excitement of the space adventure might be too much for Robin to handle.

title: Beast Boy on a Shelf
description: Santa Claus forces Beast Boy to become a spy and report on the Titans' naughty behavior.

title: Baby Mouth
description: In order to find out about his family history, Robin takes a DNA test and discovers he's from Babylon.
